These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, cycling
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, r&b
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person who likes mauve##8
2. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the fan of disco##5
3. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Sport      | cycling     | surfing      |
| Color          | mauve | fuchsia    |
| Music-Genre         | r&b   | disco |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, orange
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
House: cape-cod, cottage
There are 2 different nationalities: german, american
1. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
3. the cottage house is not to the right of the cape-cod house##8
4. the german is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Color    | apricot        | orange    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| House         | cottage | cape-cod   |
| Nationality   | german               | american  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Cigar   | dunhill       | ritmeester |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Beverage   | fanta | cola |
| Transport           | airplane        | taxi   |

