1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person who likes mauve##5
4. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
5. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Food        | cabbage | lettuce            |
